#: {{synonyms|ja|翼|tr1=tsubasa}}
# a [[fletching]] on an [[arrow]]
# {{lb|ja|sort=は|archery}} when a [[bow]] is [[strung]], the [[distance]] between the [[grip]] and the [[serving]] ([[nocking point]]) on the [[bowstring]]

